ks in the air and landing safety. The game &quot;Skater boy&quot; is so easy<br>but super fun.<p>You only need to accelerate or jump over the obstacles on the road and get the scores as possible as you can.<p>The way to play is very easy.<br>Tap the two bottoms on the screen (The right one is accelerating and the other one is jumping).Show some cool <p>tricks in the air can get extra points.<p>Features:<br>-Clear and simple pictures<br>-3 different terrains<br>-90 cool and addictive levels.<br>-Various cool tricks.<br>-More levels are coming soon. <span class="paragraph-end"></span> <a class="card-click-target" href="/store/apps/details?id=com.game.SkaterBoy" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  </div> </div>    <div class="reason-set">  <span class="stars-container"> <a href="/store/apps/details?id=com.game.SkaterBoy" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"> <div class="reason-set-star-rating">  <div class="tiny-star star-rating-non-editable-container"> <div class="current-rating" style="width: 87.28672981262207%;"></div> </div>  </div> </a> <span class="price-container"> <span class="paragraph-end"></span>  <span class="buy-button-container apps  is-price-tag" data-docid="com.game.SkaterBoy"> <div class="pon" style="display:none">1</div> <button class="price buy">  <span>Безкоштовно</span>  </button> <span style="display:none" class="consume-label"> <a style="display:none" class="consume-link id-no-nav id-track-click" data-uitype="218" href="#" target="_blank"> <span class="id-no-nav" style="display:none">Слухати</span> <span class="id-no-nav" style="display:none">Читати</span> </a> <span class="info-label" style="display:none">Лише на пристрої</span> <span class="info-label" style="display:none">Додано</span> <button style="display:none" class="consume-link id-no-nav id-watch-button id-track-click" data-uitype="218" data-video-docid="com.game.SkaterBoy">Дивитися</button> <span class="price buy id-track-click" data-uitype="221">Установлено</span> </span> <span style="d